{"lang":"es","stage":7,"title":"fuller sentences","sentences":[{"t":"Busca trabajo desde marzo.","en":"He's been looking for a job since March.","a":"n_297455af96df.mp3"},{"t":"Todo cuesta treinta euros.","en":"It all comes to thirty euros.","a":"n_dfa8138db26a.mp3"},{"t":"Comemos a la una.","en":"We eat at one.","a":"n_2ed642832c6e.mp3"},{"t":"Termino a las cinco.","en":"I finish at five.","a":"n_c0bbec5ed7ed.mp3"},{"t":"Los domingos duermo mucho.","en":"On Sundays I sleep a lot.","a":"n_0f24e17f3819.mp3"},{"t":"El sábado no trabajo.","en":"I don't work on Saturday.","a":"n_eec7ec969f62.mp3"},{"t":"Te veo el jueves.","en":"See you on Thursday.","a":"n_90f533fba732.mp3"},{"t":"¿A qué hora empezamos?","en":"What time do we start?","a":"n_9160de1f7439.mp3"},{"t":"Hoy es mi cumpleaños.","en":"Today is my birthday.","a":"n_80b3092c2f51.mp3"},{"t":"Llegas tarde otra vez.","en":"You're late again.","a":"n_b1f45caa7c64.mp3"},{"t":"¿Cuánto cuestan los dos?","en":"How much are the two of them?","a":"n_370f1ec5f38d.mp3"},{"t":"¿Por cuánto lo vendes?","en":"How much are you selling it for?","a":"n_47865876b101.mp3"},{"t":"Entrar es gratis hoy.","en":"Getting in is free today.","a":"n_2ee951c751f5.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele el estómago.","en":"My stomach hurts.","a":"n_d0944c39815c.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele la espalda.","en":"My back hurts.","a":"n_53724b507383.mp3"},{"t":"Me duelen los ojos.","en":"My eyes hurt.","a":"n_9aa92abf857c.mp3"},{"t":"Te presento a Ana.","en":"Let me introduce you to Ana.","a":"n_be67f281b3a0.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy aburrido en casa.","en":"I'm bored at home.","a":"n_11111807faad.mp3"},{"t":"Ella necesita más dinero.","en":"She needs more money.","a":"n_a60f637ded98.mp3"},{"t":"Puedo verlo más tarde.","en":"I can see it later.","a":"n_5400e37b3ed5.mp3"},{"t":"¿Vienes o te quedas?","en":"Are you coming or staying?","a":"n_7bff96cee8f9.mp3"},{"t":"Ella hace la cena.","en":"She's making dinner.","a":"n_ad14bc5ed2d8.mp3"},{"t":"Hago una pregunta rápida.","en":"I'll ask a quick question.","a":"n_6b9c9abf1dd3.mp3"},{"t":"Hice la maleta anoche.","en":"I packed my bag last night.","a":"n_901e2799026b.mp3"},{"t":"No me hagas reír.","en":"Don't make me laugh.","a":"n_bdd7a4bb5324.mp3"},{"t":"Te lo cuento luego.","en":"I'll tell you about it later.","a":"n_c0976f0e4369.mp3"},{"t":"¿Quién te lo contó?","en":"Who told you?","a":"n_509124bdf814.mp3"},{"t":"Nunca me cuentas nada.","en":"You never tell me anything.","a":"n_a37b98ed6e23.mp3"},{"t":"No conozco ese restaurante.","en":"I don't know that restaurant.","a":"n_70a7e1b8c179.mp3"},{"t":"No veo la diferencia.","en":"I don't see the difference.","a":"n_22c49acf2a8f.mp3"},{"t":"Te quiero mostrar algo.","en":"I want to show you something.","a":"n_b786644f7ffb.mp3"},{"t":"No me mires así.","en":"Don't look at me like that.","a":"n_f4395032576c.mp3"},{"t":"Trabajamos mucho esta semana.","en":"We're working a lot this week.","a":"n_bab483cd0fdb.mp3"},{"t":"¿Me pasas el pan?","en":"Can you pass me the bread?","a":"n_8260e314ed36.mp3"},{"t":"Mis amigos viven cerca.","en":"My friends live nearby.","a":"n_7be173af00dc.mp3"},{"t":"Empezamos a las cuatro.","en":"We start at four.","a":"n_4107d6311a4c.mp3"},{"t":"Hace frío en diciembre.","en":"It's cold in December.","a":"n_89a507a370e2.mp3"},{"t":"Mi reloj está mal.","en":"My watch is wrong.","a":"n_5222bd9e441f.mp3"},{"t":"Más tarde te explico.","en":"I'll explain later.","a":"n_1a8dda973678.mp3"},{"t":"Hoy me levanté tarde.","en":"I got up late today.","a":"n_47261ab708c3.mp3"},{"t":"Llegas justo a tiempo.","en":"You're right on time.","a":"n_75d7421f62af.mp3"},{"t":"¿Puedo pagar con tarjeta?","en":"Can I pay by card?","a":"n_fdb0261867ba.mp3"},{"t":"¿Dónde paro el taxi?","en":"Where do I stop the taxi?","a":"n_38bf71904443.mp3"},{"t":"Siempre pierdo el tren.","en":"I always miss the train.","a":"n_fb1337b25091.mp3"},{"t":"Me duele un diente.","en":"One of my teeth hurts.","a":"n_133ca36afe13.mp3"},{"t":"Ayer fui al cine.","en":"Yesterday I went to the movies.","a":"n_8c6a53a934c7.mp3"},{"t":"Me duelen los pies.","en":"My feet hurt.","a":"n_d3e276a383b3.mp3"},{"t":"Mírate en el espejo.","en":"Look at yourself in the mirror.","a":"n_3883fbe04563.mp3"},{"t":"Nunca lo he probado.","en":"I've never tried it.","a":"n_9a1aaeffc51b.mp3"},{"t":"¿Adónde fuiste el sábado?","en":"Where did you go on Saturday?","a":"n_322ac3580753.mp3"},{"t":"Tienes que comer algo.","en":"You have to eat something.","a":"n_5124df5c1fb6.mp3"},{"t":"No, no soy yo.","en":"No, that's not me.","a":"n_bfef6aef92aa.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy bien, ¿y tú?","en":"I'm good, and you?","a":"n_6415777197df.mp3"},{"t":"Hago lo que quiero.","en":"I do what I want.","a":"n_e04721c431ca.mp3"},{"t":"Hago lo que puedo.","en":"I do what I can.","a":"n_c0847fd8036f.mp3"},{"t":"Tienes que dormir más.","en":"You have to sleep more.","a":"n_70d527aa084f.mp3"},{"t":"¿Tienes que trabajar mañana?","en":"Do you have to work tomorrow?","a":"n_a5aa323b17c9.mp3"},{"t":"Mira lo que tengo.","en":"Look what I've got.","a":"n_90c7f3c82679.mp3"},{"t":"Sí, me duele aquí.","en":"Yes, it hurts here.","a":"n_9d6f5dfd63bb.mp3"},{"t":"Estoy cansado pero feliz.","en":"I'm tired but happy.","a":"n_42b58b2f2c6a.mp3"},{"t":"Tengo hambre, necesito comer.","en":"I'm hungry, I need to eat.","a":"n_a2eb2c079bfa.mp3"},{"t":"Me levanto y como.","en":"I get up and eat.","a":"n_4377ebe3502e.mp3"},{"t":"Quiero pedir, por favor.","en":"I'd like to order, please.","a":"n_97419113d507.mp3"},{"t":"Sé que tienes razón.","en":"I know you're right.","a":"n_ff9f78111959.mp3"},{"t":"Creo que tienes razón.","en":"I think you're right.","a":"n_01b41f3c8ab1.mp3"},{"t":"Mira, este es Carlos.","en":"Look, this is Carlos.","a":"n_a69ad6bc52d6.mp3"},{"t":"Tengo que estudiar hoy.","en":"I have to study today.","a":"n_57555288b8c6.mp3"},{"t":"No, así está bien.","en":"No, that's fine.","a":"n_761408aa727d.mp3"},{"t":"No necesito nada, gracias.","en":"I don't need anything, thanks.","a":"n_b8ca2a0224b8.mp3"},{"t":"Gracias, ¿está muy lejos?","en":"Thanks, is it very far?","a":"n_052033535dd6.mp3"},{"t":"Sé que puedo hacerlo.","en":"I know I can do it.","a":"n_0fa95bcb55f6.mp3"},{"t":"Puedes hacerlo, lo sé.","en":"You can do it, I know it.","a":"n_4a5d04bc5bf6.mp3"},{"t":"Prefiero hacerlo solo, gracias.","en":"I'd rather do it alone, thanks.","a":"n_fbe8fc3ac0ea.mp3"},{"t":"Trabajo y luego como.","en":"I work and then eat.","a":"n_d497b6d9ec4e.mp3"},{"t":"Sí, se llama Ana.","en":"Yes, her name is Ana.","a":"n_cc66644598d3.mp3"},{"t":"Tenemos que salir ya.","en":"We have to leave now.","a":"n_99204830bf4f.mp3"},{"t":"¿Tenemos que ir todos?","en":"Do we all have to go?","a":"n_389d95cb169e.mp3"},{"t":"Tienes razón, necesito descansar.","en":"You're right, I need to rest.","a":"n_df0ea6798633.mp3"},{"t":"Tienes que ver esto.","en":"You have to see this.","a":"n_5ec6b3be679b.mp3"},{"t":"La cuenta, por favor.","en":"The check, please.","a":"n_1abc4f208865.mp3"},{"t":"No, soy de México.","en":"No, I'm from Mexico.","a":"n_05ef67390614.mp3"},{"t":"Sí, es mi amiga.","en":"Yes, she's my friend.","a":"n_e904af040850.mp3"},{"t":"Sí, tengo mucha hambre.","en":"Yeah, I'm really hungry.","a":"n_583ec7f2fda3.mp3"},{"t":"Comí más que tú.","en":"I ate more than you.","a":"n_b3620cfc120d.mp3"},{"t":"Hola, me llamo Carlos.","en":"Hi, my name is Carlos.","a":"n_40012de82b4d.mp3"},{"t":"Hay que tener paciencia.","en":"You need to have patience.","a":"n_4b885232af44.mp3"},{"t":"Dile que ya voy.","en":"Tell him I'm on my way.","a":"n_dfe644f67c34.mp3"},{"t":"Dile que lo siento.","en":"Tell him I'm sorry.","a":"n_77d8e6317490.mp3"},{"t":"Mucho gusto, soy Carlos.","en":"Nice to meet you, I'm Carlos.","a":"n_b07dc362101b.mp3"},{"t":"Encantada, me llamo Ana.","en":"Nice to meet you, my name is Ana.","a":"n_217f2586addc.mp3"},{"t":"Tengo que decirte algo.","en":"I have to tell you something.","a":"n_26441d17189a.mp3"},{"t":"Busca aquí, no allí.","en":"Look here, not there.","a":"n_5bc6239846ba.mp3"},{"t":"Pagué demasiado, lo sé.","en":"I paid too much, I know.","a":"n_0b8194c11b1e.mp3"},{"t":"Creo que tengo fiebre.","en":"I think I have a fever.","a":"n_9191987593f4.mp3"}]}